      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SAVE ME GARY (8) jumped from out wide and was game in defeat last start when a 1.5 lengths second (25.83) behind Hurricane Bert at this track. Top prospect. PADDY'S WAY (5) was sent out long odds last time but rocketed out of the boxes with a fast early sectional and gave a sight before being swallowed up late, finishing a 2 length second (25.75) over 450m at this track. Winning chance. HIGH COBBER (7) settled midfield in the run and boxed on to finish there when 4th (25.86) at this track. Comes through a solid form race last start. Should be in this for a long way. BEANIE THIEF (4) was in the money last time at this track (25.88) in a Mix 6/7, finishing a 4 length third. Already a winner from this draw.",
